<h1>I Bonds for Nurses 2026</h1>
<p class="hub-crumb" style="font-family:sans-serif;font-size:0.9em;background:#f0f4ff;border-left:4px solid #3b6cf8;padding:8px 14px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;margin:14px 0;">Part of the <a href="nurse-money-hub-2026.html"><strong>Nurse Money & Investing Hub</strong></a> &mdash; browse every related guide in one place.</p>
<!-- FINANCIAL DISCLAIMER -->
<p style="font-size:0.85em;color:#888;font-style:italic;border-left:3px solid #e5e7eb;padding-left:10px;margin:8px 0 16px;">
